member.name: WS_SECURITY_KEY_TYPE
member.summary: The key type of a security token. It is used as the return type when a security token is queried about its key. It is also used to specify the required key type when requesting a security token from a security token service.

member.name: WS_SECURITY_KEY_TYPE.WS_SECURITY_KEY_TYPE_NONE
member.summary: Has no key -- it may be a bearer token such as a username/password pair.
